{"Version": "1.0.0", "LINES": [{"text": "On average, a human produces more than\n70 kilos of excrement per year.", "start": 41.16, "duration": 4.44, "ents": [], "sentiment": 0.11666666666666665}, {"text": "Globally, that represents\n550 million tonnes of waste", "start": 46.56, "duration": 3.56, "ents": [{"label_": "QUANTITY", "text": "550 million tonnes"}], "sentiment": -0.1}, {"text": "10 years ago, Bill Gates, who\nexplores the world for his foundation,", "start": 68.76, "duration": 3.96, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "10 years ago"}, {"label_": "PERSON", "text": "Bill Gates"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Nearly 700 million human\nbeings defecate outside.", "start": 80.36, "duration": 3.76, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "Nearly 700 million"}], "sentiment": 0.03333333333333333}, {"text": "It kills nearly 400,000\nchildren each year.", "start": 91.2, "duration": 3.6, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "nearly 400,000"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "each year"}], "sentiment": 0.1}, {"text": "In 2011, Bill Gates launched a\nmajor international competition", "start": 108.88, "duration": 3.4, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "2011"}, {"label_": "PERSON", "text": "Bill Gates"}], "sentiment": 0.03125}, {"text": "because, Number One, it\u00eds easier to\ntreat our waste when it\u00eds separated.", "start": 285.8, "duration": 4.56, "ents": [], "sentiment": -0.2}, {"text": "Number Two, most of the nutrients\nare concentrated in the urine.", "start": 291.12, "duration": 4.2, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "Two"}], "sentiment": 0.5}, {"text": "One afternoon,\nwe found ourselves", "start": 307.28, "duration": 2.0, "ents": [{"label_": "TIME", "text": "One afternoon"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "at one of the biggest\nsh*t factories in the world.", "start": 309.28, "duration": 2.88, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "one"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "That pile is two days' worth.", "start": 323.6, "duration": 1.52, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "two days'"}], "sentiment": 0.3}, {"text": "always brings us\nback to one question.", "start": 341.36, "duration": 2.28, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "one"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "In 1858, London was sweltering,\nand the level of the Thames,", "start": 381.76, "duration": 4.52, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "1858"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "London"}, {"label_": "ORG", "text": "Thames"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Like in Paris, which had nearly\n3,000 kilometers of sewer pipes.", "start": 419.88, "duration": 4.36, "ents": [{"label_": "GPE", "text": "Paris"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "nearly\n3,000 kilometers"}], "sentiment": 0.1}, {"text": "Everyday we produce about 1 over liter\nof urine and about 200 grams of sh*t.", "start": 447.84, "duration": 8.96, "ents": [{"label_": "QUANTITY", "text": "about 1 over"}, {"label_": "QUANTITY", "text": "about 200 grams"}, {"label_": "ORG", "text": "sh*t"}], "sentiment": -0.2}, {"text": "a businessman in Singapore\nwho, at the age of 40,", "start": 473.84, "duration": 3.28, "ents": [{"label_": "GPE", "text": "Singapore"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "the age of 40"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "So when I was 3 or 4 years\nold, we live in Kampong", "start": 492.12, "duration": 6.48, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "3 or 4 years\nold"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "Kampong"}], "sentiment": 0.11818181818181818}, {"text": "and replace it with\na fresh new one,", "start": 523.84, "duration": 2.8, "ents": [], "sentiment": 0.21818181818181817}, {"text": "Over the last 10 years,\nthe stars have aligned.", "start": 568.24, "duration": 3.24, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "the last 10 years"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "All that was true\nuntil 2 October 2014.", "start": 640.88, "duration": 3.68, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "2 October 2014"}], "sentiment": 0.35}, {"text": "At the time, of the 900\nmillion people in the world", "start": 683.56, "duration": 3.12, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "900\nmillion"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "who had no sanitary facilities,\n40% were Indian.", "start": 686.68, "duration": 4.24, "ents": [{"label_": "PERCENT", "text": "40%"}, {"label_": "NORP", "text": "Indian"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "The one which involves\nleaving the handling of poop", "start": 712.64, "duration": 2.48, "ents": [], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Had we tried to sell vegetables,\nno one would have bought them.", "start": 792.88, "duration": 4.68, "ents": [], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "that toilets are a desirable space\nand that you should have one at home", "start": 852.56, "duration": 4.2, "ents": [], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "employing more\nthan 35,000 people.", "start": 871.84, "duration": 3.0, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "35,000"}], "sentiment": 0.5}, {"text": "And five years later, on 2 October\n2019, on Gandhi\u00eds 150th birthday,", "start": 963.32, "duration": 6.04, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "five years later"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "2"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "October\n2019"}, {"label_": "ORG", "text": "Gandhi\u00eds 150th"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "He announced that no one\ndefecated outside anymore.", "start": 973.44, "duration": 3.48, "ents": [], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Today, out of the\n110 million toilets,", "start": 1013.92, "duration": 3.96, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "Today"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "110 million"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "it is anybody\u00eds guess\nwhether it is 50 million,", "start": 1018.36, "duration": 4.84, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "50 million"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "or 30 million or 80 million,\nwe do not know.", "start": 1023.88, "duration": 4.84, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "30 million"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "80 million"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "the World Bank has promised to\ndistribute 2 billion dollars to India", "start": 1031